
=======================================================================
Features
=======================================================================
- specify how to render missing values in the heatmap
- control smoothing mode by shortcuts
- disable smoothing of specific heatmap columns
- heatmap fly-over inspection 
    - cope with smoothed heatmap: show smoothed values for numeric data, 
      mixture of categories for categorical
    - show scaled values optionally?
- highlight the currently selected cluster in the heatmap to ease
  visual inspection (e.g. using a rectangle, shading the complement of
  the current cluster, etc.)
- when inspecting the dendrogram, optionally draw a horizontal line
  from the cursor across the heatmap to ease locating which
  observations belong to specific clusters
- configurable layout of dendro window components (relative/absolute
  size)
- configurable layout of windows (dendro and GUI)
- configurable dendro orientation (left-to-right, right-to-left,
  top-to-bottom, bottom-to-top)
- make axis ticks nicer: make the number of ticks proportional to the
  width of the axis on the screen 
- listen to changes to `.cluster' metadata?
- support other types of HCA inputs (return values of other function than just hclust)

